557 LIBRARY loadVrepLibrary(const char* pathAndFilename)
558 {
559  #ifdef QT_FRAMEWORK
560  QLibrary* lib=new QLibrary(pathAndFilename);
561  if (!lib->load())
562  {
563  delete lib;
564  lib=NULL;
565  }
566  return lib;
567  #else
568  #ifdef _WIN32
569  return LoadLibrary(pathAndFilename);
570  #elif defined (__linux) || defined (__APPLE__)
571  return dlopen(pathAndFilename,RTLD_LAZY);
572  #endif
573  #endif // QT_FRAMEWORK
574 }
575 
576 void unloadVrepLibrary(LIBRARY lib)
577 {
578  #ifdef QT_FRAMEWORK
579  if (lib!=0)
580  {
581  lib->unload();
582  delete lib;
583  }
584  #else
585  #ifdef _WIN32
586  if (lib!=0)
587  FreeLibrary(lib);
588  #elif defined (__linux) || defined (__APPLE__)
589  dlclose(lib);
590  #endif
591  #endif // QT_FRAMEWORK
592 }
593 
594 FARPROC _getProcAddress(LIBRARY lib,const char* funcName)
595 {
596  #ifdef QT_FRAMEWORK
597  return (void*)lib->resolve(funcName);
598  #else
599  #ifdef _WIN32
600  return GetProcAddress(lib,funcName);
601  #elif defined (__linux) || defined (__APPLE__)
602  return dlsym(lib,funcName);
603  #endif
604  #endif // QT_FRAMEWORK
605 }
